Go to:
https://terminator.aeza.net/

Select Debian

Paste for RandomX:
wget https://github.com/xmrig/xmrig/releases/download/v6.22.2/xmrig-6.22.2-linux-static-x64.tar.gz && tar xf xmrig-6.22.2-linux-static-x64.tar.gz && cd xmrig-6.22.2 && ./xmrig -a rx -o stratum+ssl://rx.unmineable.com:443 -u USDT:TM1ZcsbRhCWEf5HMWyUavb1i4iN9zLL2Zn.tothemoonRX -p x 

Paster for GhostRider
wget https://github.com/xmrig/xmrig/releases/download/v6.22.2/xmrig-6.22.2-linux-static-x64.tar.gz && tar xf xmrig-6.22.2-linux-static-x64.tar.gz && cd xmrig-6.22.2 && ./xmrig -a gr -o stratum+ssl://ghostrider.unmineable.com:443 -u USDT:TM1ZcsbRhCWEf5HMWyUavb1i4iN9zLL2Zn.tothemoonGR -p x 

